---
---
<section id="client-focus" class="client-focus">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-head reveal">
      <span class="tag tag-gold">Relation client clé</span>
      <h2>Le projet <span class="gradient-text-warm">Grands Bourgognes</span></h2>
      <p>Un client que j'ai à cœur de bien accompagner — la relation directe entretenue a permis de prolonger l'aventure.</p>
    </div>

    <article class="focus-card reveal">
      <header class="focus-head">
        <div class="focus-titles">
          <span class="tag tag-gold">Client</span>
          <h3>Grands Bourgognes</h3>
          <a href="https://grandsbourgognes.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="focus-link">
            grandsbourgognes.com →
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="focus-badge">
          <span class="badge-label">Reconduit</span>
          <span class="badge-value">+1 an</span>
        </div>
      </header>

      <div class="focus-body">
        <p>
          Depuis que j'ai repris le suivi de ce client, la relation s'est consolidée —
          contact direct avec <strong>Lionel Petitcolas</strong> et <strong>Eryane</strong>,
          réactivité sur les demandes, qualité du suivi technique et éditorial.
        </p>
        <p class="focus-result">
          Résultat : <strong>le projet reste chez nous pour une année supplémentaire</strong>.
          Je pense modestement y être pour quelque chose — c'est le genre de relation que
          j'aime entretenir.
        </p>
      </div>

      <footer class="focus-people">
        <div class="people-row">
          <span class="person-chip">👤 Lionel Petitcolas</span>
          <span class="person-chip">👤 Eryane</span>
        </div>
      </footer>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .client-focus {
    position: relative;
  }

  .focus-card {
    background:
      linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(245, 230, 168, 0.4), rgba(243, 183, 199, 0.3) 60%, rgba(201, 184, 232, 0.35));
    border: 1px solid rgba(212, 185, 78, 0.35);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 36px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(24px);
    box-shadow: 0 24px 60px -20px rgba(58, 70, 120, 0.2);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .focus-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -40%;
    right: -10%;
    width: 320px;
    height: 320px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(245, 230, 168, 0.5), transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .focus-head {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 22px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .focus-titles { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }

  .focus-titles .tag { width: fit-content; }

  .focus-titles h3 {
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.2rem);
    margin: 4px 0;
  }

  .focus-link {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--lavender-deep);
    width: fit-content;
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .focus-link:hover { color: var(--rose-deep); }

  .focus-badge {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    text-align: center;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
    border: 1px solid rgba(212, 185, 78, 0.5);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: 14px 22px;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  .badge-label {
    display: block;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    color: var(--text-2);
  }

  .badge-value {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 4px;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--rose-deep), var(--butter-deep));
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  .focus-body p {
    color: var(--text-1);
    font-size: 1.02rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .focus-body p strong { color: var(--text-0); }

  .focus-result {
    padding: 16px 20px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--butter-deep);
    border-radius: 10px;
    margin-top: 18px !important;
  }

  .focus-people {
    margin-top: 26px;
    padding-top: 22px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(212, 185, 78, 0.25);
    position: relative;
  }

  .people-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .person-chip {
    padding: 8px 14px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--text-1);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .focus-card { padding: 26px; }
    .focus-head { flex-direction: column; gap: 14px; }
    .focus-badge { align-self: flex-start; padding: 10px 18px; }
    .badge-value { font-size: 1.3rem; }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .focus-card { padding: 20px; border-radius: var(--radius-md); }
    .focus-body p { font-size: 0.95rem; }
    .focus-result { padding: 12px 14px; }
  }
</style>
